{"tid":1264934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［明日香港］支那物業管理公司爭地盤 勁過土皇帝 爽過黑社會","createTime":"2019-06-29T02:45:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T07:48:20.000Z","uid":86509,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"bef429644356edff5f524a84160ea24ea8c1ee03","tid":1264934,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:45:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2172206316257176&amp;id=265944843550009\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2172206316257176%26id%3D265944843550009&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6tTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=091a3f1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2172206316257176&amp;id=265944843550009</a><br />\n<br />\n【防暴盾藍衣人VS木棍迷彩人】<br />\n【原來是物業管理公司爭地盤】<br />\n【勁過土皇帝 爽過黑社會】<br />\n<br />\n防暴盾藍衣人大戰木棍迷彩人，打足四、五十米距離，他們不是防暴警驅散暴徒，而是物業管理公司爭地盤。山東臨沂一個屋苑的業主決定聘請新的物業管理公司，但舊公司竟然在新公司接手的當天堅守陣地，雙方大打出手，最後要警方到場調停。<br />\n<br />\n當你以為就此了事，他們就去到另一個屋苑捲土重來。業主和保安爭吵？「這車我買了，給我砸！」不肯用指定裝修公司？斷水斷電！業主立案法團？不准成立！<br />\n<br />\n天天數十個戴住口罩的紋身男拿著用報紙包住的刀巡街，令業主有家不敢回。有人直接賣樓搬屋，一了百了；也有人向物業公司遞煙送酒，叫聲領導。<br />\n<br />\n#物業管理公司<br />\n#領導<br />\n#反客為主<br />\n#掃黑除惡<br />\n#有線中國組"},{"pid":"8c012d4aeea0e1f7471943edf725e86e698b343a","tid":1264934,"uid":86509,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:46:03.000Z","msg":"大家一齊擁抱大灣區<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ad277864933bd5954b73caf6021513bdbeb9910","tid":1264934,"uid":86509,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:46:32.000Z","msg":"萬里陽光司法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07696e26d56a3533d9f6e6a6a13651c52c2da7df","tid":1264934,"uid":18245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:46:50.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>2047年 中共不死香港死。<br />\n<strong>香港最寶貴唔係個島仔，最寶貴係香港人。<br />\n邊到有大量港人邊到就係香港</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">開啟方舟計劃，建新香港！</span></span>作為香港既backup plan,現在需要各界精英加入<br />\n<br />\n歡迎入谷討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/JnVffhFDTA7KhDtjsfY58w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJnVffhFDTA7KhDtjsfY58w&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6tTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=6ad4c920\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/JnVffhFDTA7KhDtjsfY58w</a><br />\n<br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"fcf3c8de17e87c929d67dadfd2178ee8b0f4e001","tid":1264934,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:47:48.000Z","msg":"厲害了蝗的國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2af7640d4a9adf7a5619e257b704ce246bdee1","tid":1264934,"uid":86509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:49:22.000Z","msg":"點解成㗎車打爛都唔係暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6e6220f2427dcab1abc0ebd84b3f219a59c6275","tid":1264934,"uid":86509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:50:37.000Z","msg":"冇共產黨後面睇住邊夠膽咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c287f44a992282b541e3231017b8eb6991e3e9","tid":1264934,"uid":142819,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:51:49.000Z","msg":"大陸好多呢啲物管公司都係啲黑社會做的"},{"pid":"427ecf65bbd199016d5951ffe41c98ceb2c0cd5b","tid":1264934,"uid":23590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:52:21.000Z","msg":"好痴線"},{"pid":"9b8e9969cefb82bd765c6984635ae029fbbc2ca6","tid":1264934,"uid":86509,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"13c287f44a992282b541e3231017b8eb6991e3e9","tid":1264934,"uid":142819,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:51:49.000Z","msg":"大陸好多呢啲物管公司都係啲黑社會做的"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:53:13.000Z","msg":"唔奇呀<br />\n連執政黨都係黑社會去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19d16158d884f